      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need help writing an email to a customer. They bought this really expensive espresso machine from us, but the shipping is stuck in a logistics error and it's basically two weeks late now. I need to tell them what happened and apologize, but keep it professional. Can you help me draft something?",
